query:
-- Get all remaining islands without atollId
SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT CONCAT("'", p.name, "'") ORDER BY p.name SEPARATOR ', ') as island_names
FROM places p
WHERE p.type = 'island' AND p.atollId IS NULL
LIMIT 1;
